{"tid":689051,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[讓座]同意廢老專用車廂既入一入黎","createTime":"2018-06-03T19:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T04:31:41.000Z","uid":69898,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07633f001cae622e8a51756db4c426b4d52610d7","tid":689051,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:02:03.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完星期日檔案，主題係關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見巴打係咁講有廢老專用車廂，就解決到好多問題<br />\n<br />\n如果真係實行又有冇得諗呢?<br />\n正如電梯都有潛規則:左行右企<br />\n咁可唔可能製造一個廢老專用車廂呢?<br />\n<br />\n例如所有年輕人都唔上第一卡車廂，等班廢老廢中自己慢慢讓座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然繁忙時間就例外啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada9a934c61c6ef43d6a656bfc1f25f56e7302ff","tid":689051,"uid":101433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"不如唔好整坐位 個個都企<br />\n另一類就小巴 淨係可以坐"},{"pid":"52a32160899d2cd95aa2293418e5ec753fb1b7f5","tid":689051,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ada9a934c61c6ef43d6a656bfc1f25f56e7302ff","tid":689051,"uid":101433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:05:27.000Z","msg":"不如唔好整坐位 個個都企<br />\n另一類就小巴 淨係可以坐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:07:55.000Z","msg":"就係講緊港鐵唔可能冇座位，又唔撚肯cut批鬥座既同時<br />\n我地可以做到啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8d1d3d6a17c2ccbb291f5f0f43f48eee11329b","tid":689051,"uid":23247,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:09:02.000Z","msg":"要用$2優惠就一定要去專用車廂 <br />\n唔好整咗個專用車廂又走番過黎霸位 <br />\n<br />\n如果被發現用$2優惠又無用專用車廂就罰錢（又可以俾啲野俾查飛狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n或者扣起佢用$2優惠既權利<br />\n<br />\n又要納稅人資助佢$2答車 又要人放工讓位俾佢 正宗又食又拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40a0216be678e5711c677afe597c1d500273dcc","tid":689051,"uid":84869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"不如設立全企位車箱"},{"pid":"8d0e67d96b5955da3e50ee581c78a408f68804c0","tid":689051,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"一定要無扶手無座位"},{"pid":"c1611ccf43351be529d3334d3078e6cbc7acc543","tid":689051,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"你咁做唔代表班老人唔會去其他車廂批鬥 佢地覺得自己無位坐就惡哂架啦"},{"pid":"d121d5344abf2f27712ef65c20855ae40c748064","tid":689051,"uid":37876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1611ccf43351be529d3334d3078e6cbc7acc543","tid":689051,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"你咁做唔代表班老人唔會去其他車廂批鬥 佢地覺得自己無位坐就惡哂架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"呢句真, 我屋企個老人尋晚大大聲係到話D人顧住玩電話唔讓坐比佢<br />\n仲走去鬧人話佢地第時大肚都唔會有人讓坐<br />\n我「其實你只需要講聲阿伯腳痛唔企得, 可唔可以讓個位比阿伯坐咪得, 一黎就咁講野, 如果係我我會當聽唔到, 有本事你咪打我囉阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"dbe71e414bfedc3c9efbe36c5731f12b6305bca3","tid":689051,"uid":5846,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"不如整埋連登你專用車廂，出面大大隻字寫住「內有惡犬，生人勿近」"},{"pid":"3fc1a6be5fe649cbe52333c8d665ca78bc1476a5","tid":689051,"uid":119979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbe71e414bfedc3c9efbe36c5731f12b6305bca3","tid":689051,"uid":5846,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"不如整埋連登你專用車廂，出面大大隻字寫住「內有惡犬，生人勿近」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"連登你"},{"pid":"8ef2edc5646c929116f0265372f29cebd4b80990","tid":689051,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc1a6be5fe649cbe52333c8d665ca78bc1476a5","tid":689051,"uid":119979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"